{"tid":11010,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"telegram bot下載youtube歌","createTime":"2016-11-29T06:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T12:15:23.000Z","uid":11571,"like":172,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ca257194c58558230dca540ec89e4c92f00dae42","tid":11010,"uid":11571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"之前開左活動台 家下再貼係創意台 宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寫完無人用好慘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家好,我屎忽痕整左個telegram bot, 幫手下載youtube歌做mp3<br />\n<br />\n用法: 貼條youtube link俾佢,佢down完會send俾你<br />\n<br />\nAndroid down完禁&quot;save to Music&quot; 會放係Internal Storage-&gt;Music<br />\n<br />\n俾下comment 試玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/u2bu_mp3_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fu2bu_mp3_bot&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=63a25572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/u2bu_mp3_bot</a><br />\ntelegram id: @u2bu_mp3_bot<br />\n<br />\n過往share既音樂可以禁&quot;Shared Media&quot; --&gt; &quot;Shared Music&quot; 搵返<br />\niOS 無得down返落部機,但可以用telegram個player:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/f4ykniju\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff4ykniju&h=0937d7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n@youtube&lt;空白&gt;可以直接search youtube link俾bot down歌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/z2m0lqe8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz2m0lqe8&h=ca918b89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n@u2bu_mp3_bot&lt;空白&gt;可以睇最近D人 down過咩歌, 打/suggest可以拎歌單,當係recommendation<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/eyh5pqt0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feyh5pqt0&h=abf86c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/080750_a9a9a11eeea97eabe51680f38b59301b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F080750_a9a9a11eeea97eabe51680f38b59301b.jpg&h=2eed5e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾有用<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多鬼餘"},{"pid":"178835457872e672b7f7d0d6023f39b3cb341d7e","tid":11010,"uid":21696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"推一推  應該幾有用"},{"pid":"0f387b48b80b0769b37e68afe7d4a487de38fc67","tid":11010,"uid":3831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾撚正"},{"pid":"2b445bdf3a23c07ec9240e6553141b26c7e35a0c","tid":11010,"uid":33301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:54:32.000Z","msg":"有無Down埋片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fc5e4a8a481dae046a8bea525f78b43b60e68c","tid":11010,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正"},{"pid":"43414d05bb9c9f08504751b23c6fed9b85385fbd","tid":11010,"uid":1247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"唔錯喎 其實係咪接去個youtube to MP3 個網到？"},{"pid":"8f02fe9342544d7e18760b393f8dc338076f8155","tid":11010,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"之前用過幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7252ca7c7cd17e36845d4acc03d05e1e2c2c